1. Brief von Julie Gundert auf einem angeklebten Zettel.
.fo +
My dear Frederic

I would like to know how is your health I do not think you are well, please
tell me all about it, do you feel perhaps the cold much so that you should
be dressed wormer? tell me every thing in your next.

Seifried is not well, a good deal of palpitations and uneasiness. I will
visit today.

I write purposly to ask you to send me your wash next Saturday 16, in one
box both your wash, if the omnibus was not going send it by Beisser al-
though he asks as much as per post
